{"tid":1597244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"登報紙一日就夠籌夠，告黑警一星期都未夠數呀","createTime":"2019-09-27T01:03:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T02:26:49.000Z","uid":80972,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"a06a6e01df5934e98d089292743ee8d804ff1173","tid":1597244,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:03:22.000Z","msg":"眾籌目標一千萬，而家一星期到5百萬ja!<br />\n告得入就有案例，同埋賠款放返入去個pool到，更多受害者可以告黑警呀!<br />\n大家推呀!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n捐款傳送門<br />\n揀返捐去黎俾「<span style=\"color: red;\">反濫權大控訴眾籌計劃</span>」，咪捐錯俾社民連<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.lsd.org.hk/donate/?fbclid=IwAR20wt2wEGMi3HQKKY2rsQ7RL--jD6V7dwr9OFtVLJ_wd-vk2YOaS1F5L4g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lsd.org.hk%2Fdonate%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR20wt2wEGMi3HQKKY2rsQ7RL--jD6V7dwr9OFtVLJ_wd-vk2YOaS1F5L4g&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYi9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=d6563bbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.lsd.org.hk/donate/?fbclid=IwAR20wt2wEGMi3HQKKY2rsQ7RL--jD6V7dwr9OFtVLJ_wd-vk2YOaS1F5L4g</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W3MZzBW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW3MZzBW.jpg&h=d7faa3d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n徐子見遭警濫捕　入稟索償 (全文)<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20190927&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20776252\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190927%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20776252&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYi9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=03869222\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190927%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20776252&h=b5b46f5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20190927&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20776252</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】再有市民入稟向警方索償。東區區議員徐子見表示，月初在柴灣站協助街坊離開，當時並無作任何衝擊或叫喧，但突然遭防暴警察無理拘捕並扣留近24小時。他昨日正式入稟法院，向拘捕他的警員本人提出民事索償。<span style=\"color: red;\">他又呼籲公眾捐款支持反濫權眾籌計劃，承諾若自己索償成功也會捐出賠償金</span>。<br />\n<br />\n徐子見昨日透過資深大律師潘熙等多名律師，正式入稟控告當天拘捕他的警員徐浩賢（警員編號17172）。入稟狀要求法庭宣告，該次行動是非法拘捕、非法扣留、非法搜身及非法沒收財產，違反《基本法》及《香港人權法案》；又要求警員交還相關財產及作賠償。<br />\n<br />\n徐子見早前聯同其他幾名警暴受害人，發起「反濫權大控訴眾籌計劃」，向市民籌錢以支付包括本案在內的民事訴訟費用。他向記者強調，自己沒有被打已算是幸運的一人，但許多年輕人都遭受警察濫用暴力，心理壓力好大，「我都接觸到好多後生仔有情緒問題」，而現時並無有效的監管制度，因此他才希望透過民事訴訟向法庭取回公道。<span style=\"color: red;\">徐表示，若最終勝訴獲得賠償金，自己只會保留一元作紀念，其餘金額會全數捐給眾籌基金幫助其他受害者。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立場報導「反濫權大控訴眾籌計劃」<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/10-%E5%90%8D%E8%AD%A6%E6%9A%B4%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%B3%E4%BA%BA%E7%99%BC%E8%B5%B7%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C-%E6%93%AC%E8%88%88%E8%A8%9F%E5%90%91%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E7%B4%A2%E5%84%9F-%E6%9C%89%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E8%A2%AB%E5%8A%A0%E6%8E%A7%E7%BD%AA/?fbclid=IwAR2w3tsaLYR2kZ9NV6yrRDYdTMnX_zoJ2PzOmqslsiVL-p7GQjEnh8r2wII\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F10-%25E5%2590%258D%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C-%25E6%2593%25AC%25E8%2588%2588%25E8%25A8%259F%25E5%2590%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E5%2584%259F-%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25BF%2583%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%25BA%2596%25E5%2582%2599%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%258E%25A7%25E7%25BD%25AA%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2w3tsaLYR2kZ9NV6yrRDYdTMnX_zoJ2PzOmqslsiVL-p7GQjEnh8r2wII&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYi9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=985a0fec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F10-%25E5%2590%258D%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C-%25E6%2593%25AC%25E8%2588%2588%25E8%25A8%259F%25E5%2590%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E5%2584%259F-%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25BF%2583%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%25BA%2596%25E5%2582%2599%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%258E%25A7%25E7%25BD%25AA%2F%3Ffbclid%3